`O(N)` time solution
Compute sum for the first element. Continue computing sum for others maintaining sliding window
```
class Solution {
    public int[] decrypt(int[] code, int k) {
        int n = code.length;
        int[] answer = new int[n];

        if (k == 0) {
            return answer;
        }

        int sum = 0;
        for (int idx = (n + k) % n, move = -k / Math.abs(k); idx != 0; idx = (idx + move) % n) {
            sum += code[idx];
        }

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            answer[i] = sum;

            if (k < 0) {
                sum -= code[(n + k + i) % n];
                sum += code[i];
            } else {
                sum -= code[(i + 1) % n];
                sum += code[(i + k + 1) % n];
            }
        }

        return answer;
    }
}
```

