Maintain number of `a` from left and number of `b` from right. Can be solved in `O(1)` space. Here is `O(N)` space solution

```
class Solution {
    public int minimumDeletions(String s) {
        int n = s.length();
        int[] counts = new int[n + 1];

        for (int i = n - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
            counts[i] = counts[i + 1];
            if (s.charAt(i) == 'a') {
                counts[i]++;
            }
        }

        int counter = 0;
        int answer = counts[0];

        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            if (s.charAt(i) == 'b') counter++;
            answer = Math.min(answer, counter + counts[i + 1]);
        }

        return answer;
    }
}
```

