After adding logs in the code, there is one impartant thing for the `visitedIdx` is that : 
```
visitedIdx  * *MUST* * contains the directions, because the same index can be visited both forward and backward, if we simply check the index without direction, we will lose the half possiblity. which can cause the result to -1.

