# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
  Here to solve this problem using Recursive 
  First we start Recurisve function with start = 0
  We have to two moves :
    1. go from start to start + forwardJumb
    2. go from start to start - backwardJumb
 But here we make boolean called isBack to make sure we do not 
 Make the second move twice , and check the current state not less than zero or greater than greatest move = 7000 and this 
state not forbidden

# Complexity
- Time complexity:
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->
