# Intuition
We need to try more ways in which we distrubute the repeating numbers, because we can distribute them in more ways but not all of them will satisfy all customers.

# Approach
Create a histogram(count how many times each number was seen) and we will try to satisfy all customers while going through the histogram, once we have a good match we try to solve using that number from the histogram as modified, if that doesn't work, we go back, revert the change and try another permutation.

# Complexity
