**Synopsis:**

Insert each `k`<sup>th</sup> value into an array of strings `A`, and return the result `res` of the monotonically increasing `i`<sup>th</sup> index of adjacent non-empty string values in `A`.

---

*Kotlin*
```
class OrderedStream(N_: Int) {
    private var i = 0
    private var N = N_
    private var A = MutableList<String>(N) { "" }
    fun insert(k: Int, value: String): List<String> {
        var res = mutableListOf<String>()
        A[k - 1] = value  // -1 for 0-based indexing
        while (i < N && 0 < A[i].length)
            res.add(A[i++])
        return res
    }
}
```

