occording to 1st rule : we can swap any two char at any number of time so if the cnt of all char in string word1 and word2 is same then string will be accepted .(there must not present any new char in word2 that is not present in word1)
on aplying 2nd rule : we can change the we can convert one char into other . so if any two charcter frequncy is difference then if possible then convert them .

